# Mailu configuration for chungu (local domain until real domain is available)
# [Flow: Domain/Network 설정 -> 계정/비밀번호 -> TLS -> SMTP/IMAP 포트]

###################################
# Common configuration variables
###################################
# Main mail domain
DOMAIN=chungu.local

# Hostnames for which this server should handle mail
HOSTNAMES=mail.chungu.local

# Postmaster address (required)
POSTMASTER=admin@chungu.local

# Secret key for sessions/cookies
SECRET_KEY=mfhMPnG7sZ9jQL3wXvT5cYkB8dN2pR6aF4eH1uJ0oL7iK9gQ2sW4xV1bC3nM5t

# Subnet for the docker network
SUBNET=192.168.203.0/24

# Password scheme for hashed passwords
PASSWORD_SCHEME=blf-crypt

###################################
# Optional features
###################################
# Webmail type
WEBMAIL=none
WEB_ADMIN=/admin
WEB_WEBMAIL=/
WEB_API=/api

# Antivirus (disabled to save resources)
ANTIVIRUS=none

# Antispam (disabled to save resources)
ANTISPAM=none

# WebDAV
WEBDAV=none

# FTS
FULL_TEXT_SEARCH=none

# Web UI
ADMIN=true

# API token (not used by Supabase)
API_TOKEN=none

###################################
# Mail settings
###################################
# Message size limit in bytes (50MB)
MESSAGE_SIZE_LIMIT=50000000

# Max attachment size (50MB)
MAX_ATTACHMENT_SIZE=50000000

# TLS flavor
# "mail" uses self-signed cert in ./certs; change to "letsencrypt" for real domain
TLS_FLAVOR=mail

# Ports the front container listens on (587=SMTP submission)
PORTS=25,80,587,465,993,995,4190

# Max outbound relay count
RELAYNETS=

# Relay host (leave empty for direct delivery)
RELAYHOST=

# DKIM selector
DKIM_SELECTOR=mail

# DMARC reporting
DMARC_RUA=
DMARC_RUF=

###################################
# Advanced settings
###################################
COMPOSE_PROJECT_NAME=mailu

# Log level
LOG_LEVEL=WARNING

# Hardened malloc (disabled for compatibility)
# LD_PRELOAD=/usr/lib/libhardened_malloc.so

# Automatic admin creation
INITIAL_ADMIN_ACCOUNT=admin
INITIAL_ADMIN_DOMAIN=chungu.local
INITIAL_ADMIN_PW=JDg629714!@

# Real IP header
REAL_IP_FROM=192.168.203.0/24

# Disable IPv6 (not needed for local network)
DISABLE_IPV6=true
